[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a rotten hand, and many players would just pass 1NT.

But SOUTH figures that having NORTH play any 4-4 fit would be better than 1NT so 
he bids 2\C, Stayman. This is called "Garbage Stayman", and you can see why.

NORTH bids 2\H and SOUTH passes. He would have passed 
either 2\S or 2\D also.}

